# LOCAL MARKET DOMINATION - ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and customize with your values
#
# REQUIRED:     Must be set, app will not start without these values
# OPTIONAL:     Can be empty/omitted for local development
# PRODUCTION:   Only needed for production deployments
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

